  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      153.38,
      473.69,
      201.62
    ],
    "text": "Advisory for the low pressure area in the vicinity of Sri Lanka. Issued by the Natural Hazards Early Warning Centre, Department of Meteorology. Issued at 3.00 p.m. on 13 May 2026",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      12.0,
      15.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      206.3,
      306.27,
      244.97
    ],
    "text": "PLEASE BE AWARE!",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      8.039999961853027,
      9.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      258.5,
      542.73,
      304.13
    ],
    "text": "The low-pressure area located northeast of the Sri Lanka, still persist. this system is expected to move away from Sri Lanka and gradually weaken during the next 48 hours. Therefore, the prevailing showery and windy conditions around the island are expected to continue.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      325.25,
      542.49,
      354.05
    ],
    "text": "Further, strong winds and rough seas can be expected over the deep and shallow sea areas around the island, as well as over the deep sea areas of the Bay of Bengal.",
    "fonts": [
